Posted: June 16, 2022
Expect a great game. I don’t know why, but I literally knew from the trailer that the game would be just superb and I was not mistakenю

Pros:
- Excellent visual style and sound design;
— High-quality bitmap with characters from my childhood;
— Good old cartoon April O'Neil design;
— Many levels and opponents;
— Ability to play together in multiplayer;
— 7 playable characters;
— Low price.

Minuses:
— Bugs (which is predictable and fixable);
— Multiplayer sometimes lags (I got 250-400 ping usually), idk how it still feels playable.

I'm just delighted with the final version of the game, they will play it and I don't regret the purchase at all.
